name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Goku Ultra Instinct Universe Dragon Ball Live Wallpaper

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Unleash Goku’s unstoppable Ultra Instinct form on your Chrome tab with this intense Dragon Ball Super live wallpaper! 🌌🔥💥

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Embrace the raw power of Goku in his Ultra Instinct form with this epic live wallpaper. Featuring Goku radiating energy against a cosmic backdrop, this extension brings the fierce battles and awe-inspiring moments of Dragon Ball Super right to your new tab. Perfect for Dragon Ball fans, this live wallpaper immerses you in the legendary series every time you open a new tab, showcasing Goku’s ultimate transformation.

Key Features
🖼️ Live Wallpaper: Feel the power of Ultra Instinct Goku with stunning visuals that pulse with energy.
🔗 Customizable Site Shortcuts: Set your own shortcuts to quickly access your favorite sites.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Search the web directly from your Goku-themed tab.
🕒 Clock & Date Display: Track time and date with a sleek display that complements the design.
🔗 Quick Access Links: Easily locate “Remove Extension” and “More Extensions” in the lower left corner.
Dive into the Dragon Ball Super universe and experience Goku’s Ultra Instinct transformation every day. This extension combines breathtaking art with essential features to make each new tab an adventure.
